replies.body:
@Vspleck: ye mate.

@Emdon: Once again, any movie mooch is in!
                 amas are god
                 Soccer is love.

@frosted: sure mate.
  
 @Snow: I originally bought this as a shared account for multiple of my friends and I to share. I wanted the name to relate to my own account, poptyler945, so I took the first three letters, pop, and decided to put that in the name. Then I thought of other stuff to add to it that would relate to my friends. Most of my friends plan to be within the medical field when they get older, so I decided to go with the word "doctor," but then I thought "docta" sounded cooler. After that, I put those together to come up with "DoctaPop." Then my friends later bought their own accounts so I changed the password and made the sign-in require my email and started to use this account more as I liked the name.
